<HEADLINE> Nasdaq Shows New Stock Quote System </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	NEW YORK (AP) -- The Nasdaq Stock Market unveiled a new stock  
quote display system Tuesday designed to improve investor access to 
the best prices for the 5,000 stocks listed on the Nasdaq's 
computerized trading system. 
