<HEADLINE> Americans Urged To Avoid Indonesia </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	WASHINGTON (AP) -- The State Department is urging U.S. citizens  
to defer nonemergency travel to Indonesia and says those who travel 
to that country should exercise extreme caution. 
</P>
<P>
