<HEADLINE> Devils Get Sutton Back From Caps </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	EAST RUTHERFORD, N.J. (AP) -- The New Jersey Devils reacquired  
Ken Sutton on Tuesday, getting the defenseman back from the 
Washington Capitals for future considerations. 
</P>
<P>
	Sutton, claimed by Washington in the NHL Waiver Draft last  
